  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK958">
<l>nalattiṉka ṇāriṉmai tōṉṟi ṉavaṉaik</l>
<l>kulattiṉka ṇaiyap paṭum</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one of a good family betrays want of affection, his descent from it will be called in question.</l>
